      <t>OPC Unified Architecture (OPC UA) is a data exchange specification that provides interoperability in industrial automation. With the arrival of Industry 4.0, it is of great importance to implement the exchange of semantic information utilizing OPC UA Transmitting in CoAP. This document provides some transmission methods for message of OPC UA over CoAP.</t>
